entities.text: FINITE STRING Newsletter Minutes of the Previous Meeting Program Committee Report Local Arrangements Committee Report Nominating Committee Report

abstractContent.text: Ray Perrault reported that 113 people had pre-registered for the conference.
He expressed his particular appreciation for the support provided by his students in helping with local arrangements.
[The final figures for attendance are: 138 registrants, including 26 students; 21 new members were added to ACL; more than 100 people attended the banquet.]
